function isRaceLeaderFor15Races() {
  const raceData = data['data'];
  const raceLeaders = [];
  let raceLeaderIndex = -1;
  let raceLeaderName = '';
  for (let i = 0; i < raceData.length; i++) {
    if (raceData[i][3] !== '') {
      raceLeaderIndex = i;
      raceLeaderName = raceData[i][3];
    }
    if (raceLeaderIndex >= 0 && raceData[i][2] === '-') {
      if (raceData[i][4] !== raceLeaderName) {
        break;
      }
    } else {
      const raceNumber = i + 1; // Adjust for zero-based indexing
      if (raceNumber > 14) { // Only consider races after the first 15
        continue;
      }
      raceLeaders.push({
        row_index: raceLeaderIndex,
        column_name: 'race leader'
      });
    }
  }

  return {
    answer: isRaceLeaderFor15Races() ? 'TRUE' : 'FALSE',
    relevant_cells: isRaceLeaderFor15Races() ? raceLeaders : []
  };
}
